# Sample HTTP requests for /api/embed and /api/search endpoints
# Ensure the Next.js app is running on http://localhost:3000
# Set GEMINI_API_KEY in your .env file and configure Supabase

### Embed text into the vector store
POST http://localhost:3000/api/embed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. This is a sample sentence for embedding.",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "test",
    "category": "sample"
  }
}

###

### Embed another text for variety
POST http://localhost:3000/api/embed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Artificial intelligence is transforming the world. Machine learning models are becoming more powerful.",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "test",
    "category": "ai"
  }
}

###

### Search for similar texts
POST http://localhost:3000/api/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "brown fox",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### Search for AI-related texts
POST http://localhost:3000/api/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "artificial intelligence",
  "topK": 2
}

###

### Search with default topK
POST http://localhost:3000/api/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "machine learning"
}